title: Counter-Strike 1.6 RedBull [ Red Game ] [ Steam RIP ]
description:
ScreenShot of the GUI menu : http://i.imgur.com/0w4jLD5.png

Counter-Strike 1.6 RedBull is a modification based on the original Counter-Strike 1.6 game . In CS 1.6 Nebula all weapons skins and players models was modified . The maps textures are default , as in the original game !

You can play at HIGH FPS and without LAG ! 
Easy installer path , just 274Mb HDD installer size .
Ultra HD weapons skins and players models !
The latests RevEmu to play as a Steam player !
You can join on steam and no-steam servers .
You can choose on which server you want to play from 'Internet' server list tab !
This client comes with the latest bots !
The game works offline and multiplayer !
